README.md
input                                                     processing                                                                      output                                               
                                                                                                                                            		Prompt to the user to input Product Description.  
 Get Product description -from user (String productName)                                                                                                                                        
                                                           Received and store the Product description on productName String variable                                                            
                                                                                                                                           Prompt to the user to input Product Price.           
 Get Product Price -from user (Double productPrice)                                                                                                                                             
                                                           Received and store the Product Price on productPrice Double variable                                                                 
                                                                                                                                           Prompt to the user to input Tax Rate.                
 Get Tax rate -from user (Double taxRate)                                                                                                                                                       
                                                           Received and store the Tax amount on taxRate Double variable                                                                         
                                                                                                                                           Prompt user to enter more Products                   
 If the user wants more product item(yes)                                                                                                                                                       
                                                           Received and store the ProductName,ProductPrice and Tax amount variable again                                                        
 If user chooses no                                                                                                                                                                             
                                                           Add the price of the each Product item to the total amount                                                                           
                                                           Apply tax rate to total amount (tax rate * total amount)                                                                             
                                                                                                                                           Display total amount(double totalAmount)             